---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — BoardLab Pro">
  <Navbar lang={lang} />
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-white pt-24 pb-16">
    <article class="prose prose-slate mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500">Last updated: March 18, 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>Z Electrónica UY ("the Company", "we", "us") operates BoardLab Pro. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>Account and Payment Information</h3>
      <p>When you purchase a Pro subscription, payment is handled by <a href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lemon Squeezy</a> (our merchant of record). We receive your name, email address, and subscription status. We do not store credit card numbers or payment details — these are managed entirely by Lemon Squeezy.</p>

      <h3>Application Data</h3>
      <p>Your PCB measurement data, boardview files, and project files are stored <strong>locally on your device</strong>. We do not access, collect, or transmit this data unless you explicitly use cloud sync features.</p>

      <h3>AI Diagnosis</h3>
      <p>When you use the AI-powered diagnosis feature, relevant measurement data is sent to our AI service provider for analysis. This data is used solely to generate your diagnosis and is not stored or used for training purposes.</p>

      <h3>Usage Analytics</h3>
      <p>We may collect anonymous usage statistics (feature usage, crash reports) to improve the Software. This data does not include personal information or project data.</p>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To provide and maintain the Software and Pro features</li>
        <li>To process subscriptions and communicate about your account</li>
        <li>To provide AI-powered diagnosis when requested</li>
        <li>To improve the Software based on anonymous usage patterns</li>
        <li>To send important updates about the Software (security patches, major releases)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share data only with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Lemon Squeezy:</strong> Payment processing and subscription management</li>
        <li><strong>AI Service Provider:</strong> Measurement data for diagnosis (only when you initiate a diagnosis)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Account information is retained for the duration of your subscription plus a reasonable period for record-keeping. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.</p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of non-essential communications</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>BoardLab Pro is not intended for use by children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions or data requests, contact us at <a href="mailto:zelectronicauy@gmail.com">zelectronicauy@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
